   Living In Indiana
   What makes Indiana such a special state in which to live? Whether it is
   visiting parks during our four distinct beautiful seasons or catching a
   major sporting event, Indiana has it all. The Hoosier state is truly
   the crossroads of America.

   Communities
          Visit one or several of Indiana's communities and begin to
          understand the meaning of Hoosier hospitality!

   Education
          Whether your child is going to kindergarten or college, this
          site will provide you with the information you need for your
          child's educational future.

   Voting
          Looking for election information? Let this site provide you with
          the information you'll need to vote in Indiana.

   Just for Fun
          From the exciting nightlife in downtown Indianapolis, to hiking
          the rolling hills of southern Indiana, to relaxing on the shores
          of Lake Michigan, find out what Hoosiers do "just for fun."

   Transportation
          Learn more about getting around in Indiana. Avoid construction
          delays, find out where you'll encounter toll-road fees, and much
          more. You can also renew your vehicle registration online!

   Safety & Health
          Discover a wealth of information about health and safety issues
          in Indiana. You can also find safety tips on a variety of
          topics.

   Environmental
          From recycling to forestry, Hoosiers are taking steps to ensure
          that our grandchildren will have a clean environment in which to
          play, hunt, and fish. Learn more about what you can do to
          conserve Indiana's natural habitats and resources.


